---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro'

const languageSkills = [
  { name: 'Python', icon: 'python/python-original' },
  { name: 'JavaScript', icon: 'javascript/javascript-original' },
  { name: 'C++', icon: 'cplusplus/cplusplus-original' },
  { name: 'C#', icon: 'csharp/csharp-original' },
  { name: 'Go', icon: 'go/go-original-wordmark' },
  { name: 'Swift', icon: 'swift/swift-original' },
  { name: 'Vue.js', icon: 'vuejs/vuejs-original' },
  { name: 'React', icon: 'react/react-original' },
  { name: 'Django', icon: 'django/django-plain' },
  { name: 'Tailwind CSS', icon: 'tailwindcss/tailwindcss-original' },
]

const infrastructureSkills = [
  { name: 'Linux', icon: 'linux/linux-original' },
  { name: 'Windows', icon: 'windows11/windows11-original' },
  { name: 'Docker', icon: 'docker/docker-original' },
  { name: 'Git', icon: 'git/git-original' },
  { name: 'Nginx', icon: 'nginx/nginx-original' },
]
---

<Layout
  title="關於 CHIEN"
  description="CHIEN 的個人介紹，包含學習背景、技能、網路技術與資訊安全興趣，以及目前參與的實習與社群經歷。"
  pageType="profile"
  wide
>
  <section class="border-b border-foreground/10 py-10 sm:py-12">
    <div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <p class="mb-5 font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-accent">
          About / Profile
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold leading-none text-foreground sm:text-7xl">CHIEN</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-xl/8 font-medium text-foreground sm:text-2xl/9">
          把網路、資安與系統問題，整理成可以理解、重現與持續維護的實作。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-7 max-w-2xl space-y-4 text-base/7 text-foreground/68 sm:text-lg/8">
          <p>
            你也可以叫我「謙」，不過在社群裡，大家通常叫我「柴柴」或「柴」。我出生於台灣，目前是<strong
              class="font-semibold text-foreground">資工系學生</strong
            >。
          </p>
          <p>
            我喜歡探索複雜系統背後的運作原理，也會將一路上的嘗試、踩過的坑，以及解決問題的過程記錄在這個 Blog 中。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-10 grid gap-6 border-t border-foreground/10 pt-8 md:grid-cols-[minmax(9rem,0.45fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] md:gap-10 lg:mt-12"
    >
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-accent">Current focus</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-foreground/65">現在進行中的事</p>
      </div>
      <dl class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-0">
        <div
          class="border-t border-foreground/10 pt-4 sm:border-l sm:border-t-0 sm:px-6 sm:pt-0"
        >
          <dt class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-accent">01 / NETWORK</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-sm/6 text-foreground/68">
            運營個人自治系統 <strong class="font-semibold text-foreground"
              >AS215934</strong
            >，研究 BGP 路由協議
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-t border-foreground/10 pt-4 sm:border-l sm:border-t-0 sm:px-6 sm:pt-0"
        >
          <dt class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-accent">02 / WORK</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-sm/6 text-foreground/68">
            在瀚霖智動銷售科技實習，負責全端開發、系統維運與資安
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-t border-foreground/10 pt-4 sm:border-l sm:border-t-0 sm:pl-6 sm:pt-0"
        >
          <dt class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-accent">03 / COMMUNITY</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-sm/6 text-foreground/68">
            曾參與 SITCON 志工、副組長與副召、總召
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16" aria-labelledby="skills-heading">
    <div class="mb-9 max-w-2xl">
      <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-accent">Toolbox</p>
      <h2 id="skills-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground sm:text-3xl">
        技能與工具
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-10">
      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold text-foreground/68">
          Languages & Frameworks
        </h3>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-6">
          {
            languageSkills.map((skill) => (
              <li class="flex min-h-24 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-foreground/10 p-3 text-center transition-colors hover:border-accent/35">
                <img
                  src={`https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/${skill.icon}.svg`}
                  alt=""
                  class="size-8 object-contain"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-foreground/75">{skill.name}</span>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold text-foreground/68">
          Systems & Infrastructure
        </h3>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-6">
          {
            infrastructureSkills.map((skill) => (
              <li class="flex min-h-24 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-foreground/10 p-3 text-center transition-colors hover:border-accent/35">
                <img
                  src={`https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/${skill.icon}.svg`}
                  alt=""
                  class="size-8 object-contain"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-foreground/75">{skill.name}</span>
              </li>
            ))
          }
          <li
            class="flex min-h-24 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-foreground/10 p-3 text-center transition-colors hover:border-accent/35"
          >
            <img
              src="/icons/bgp.svg"
              alt=""
              class="size-8 object-contain"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-foreground/75">BGP</span>
          </li>
          <li
            class="flex min-h-24 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-foreground/10 p-3 text-center transition-colors hover:border-accent/35"
          >
            <img
              src="/icons/networking.svg"
              alt=""
              class="size-8 object-contain"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-foreground/75">網路維運</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="grid gap-8 border-t border-foreground/10 py-12 sm:py-16 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:items-end"
  >
    <div>
      <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-accent">Contact</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground sm:text-3xl">聊聊技術或有趣的專案</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-foreground/68">
        想討論網路技術、資安或任何有趣的專案，都歡迎直接聯絡我。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-5 gap-y-3 text-sm font-semibold">
      <a href="mailto:hi@chien.dev">Email</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/qian403" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >GitHub</a
      >
      <a href="https://t.me/qian50" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Telegram</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
